#

One-Pot Borscht with Ground Beef

60 min
$12.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

dairy

Dietary Tags:

low-carbhigh-protein

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Main

Tags:

heartysoupeasycomfort food

Description

A hearty and vibrant beet soup infused with tender ground beef, perfect for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • beets: 2 cups, peeled and grated
  • cabbage: 2 cups, shredded
  • carrot: 1, shredded
  • onion: 1, diced
  • ground beef: 1 pound
  • potatoes: 2, diced
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • sour cream: for serving
  • fresh dill: for garnish
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • paprika: 1 teaspoon
